<h1>MINI ECU</h1>

Gas model engine monitoring unit.

<h3>Connectors</h3>
<h4>XP1 Engine sensors</h4>
<ul>
<li> AVCC — +3.3 for analog sensors (if needed)
<li> THERM — input for NTC 10k grounded to AGND
<li> OIL_PRES — input for analog oil pressure sensor (resistance type, optional)
<li> AGND — ground for analog sensors (connected to GND)
<li> RPM_IN — signal from ignition hall sensor
<li> STARTER — open drain output for starter relay (optional)
</ul>

<h4>XP2 Fuel flow sensor</h4>
<ul>
<li> PULSE — signal from flow sensor
<li> VCC — +3.3V for supply hall sensor
<li> GND — ground
</ul>

<h4>XP3 Data IO</h4>
<ul>
<li> VCC — +2.7 .. +5 V supply for isolator IC
<li> TXD — isolated UART TX
<li> RXD — isolated UART RX
<li> GND — isolated from main ground
</ul>

<h4>XP4 Power/Kill switch</h4>
<ul>
<li> V_IGN — switch output for ignition module
<li> GND_IGN — ground for ignition module
<li> V_BAT — ignition battery positive terminal (+)
<li> GND_BAT — battery negative terminal
</ul> 
